{"tid":1524073,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"千其唔好攪到地鐵d 廣告，好貴嫁","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T05:28:08.000Z","uid":1883,"like":218,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"627d722bfc9b4939aa1f9f3af7947cac5cab0e5a","tid":1524073,"uid":1883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:37:22.000Z","msg":"小弟作為個marketer 最驚最驚就係自己既廣告出事 近期我公司想落廣告<br />\n<br />\n得知最近各品牌都唔敢落TVC轉左落戶外廣告 而最受歡迎既就緊係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">狗鐵既廣告位</span></strong>啦<br />\n<br />\n聽講<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廣告佔狗鐵唔小既收入</span></span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n而家狗鐵係有戶外廣告公司幫佢地接廣告 收入再分成 狗鐵坐係到就有錢分<br />\n<br />\n真係好驚好驚會有人噴污糟或者破壞我地啲靚靚廣告嫁！<br />\n<br />\n污糟左我地又要花十幾期印過，洗多幾十萬<br />\n你知啦 佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">一個廣告位成百幾萬</span> 如果啲品牌驚左唔落咁點算<br />\n<br />\n咁狗鐵咪無左好多收入？<br />\n<br />\n如果<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">噴左句光復香港時代革命嘅仲死</span></span><br />\n到時以為我個品牌有政治取向點算，以後都唔敢落廣告<br />\n<br />\n一諗起就好驚 大家千其唔好呀！"},{"pid":"93cf0bceade7878d1bcd19ea86bd5e80b79c4433","tid":1524073,"uid":1883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:38:06.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"a4a59d74b7192ee9d78b99fdeb9304fc0748fce8","tid":1524073,"uid":1883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:38:27.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"8e3b4ffdbdcee42d16e23f2dd3990b4ec6958f8f","tid":1524073,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d75782ea46db0536f7810485a04f016b625aefd","tid":1524073,"uid":308507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:38:39.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"a9c722ecab1165af9e3b517a3d13e2d3fcd628c6","tid":1524073,"uid":85381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:38:52.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"35ec7e6c0397ef9b9a6a8577694ad947f404